<font color="white">MUSIC CONTINUES</font>

01:42.280 --> 01:44.840
<font color="white"># Come down</font>

01:44.840 --> 01:47.960
<font color="white"># Off of your pomp and pride</font>

01:49.800 --> 01:52.800
<font color="white"># Now there's a time for you</font>

01:52.800 --> 01:55.200
<font color="white"># There's a time for me</font>

01:57.240 --> 01:59.120
<font color="cyan"># Leave your man's business</font>

02:01.160 --> 02:03.200
<font color="cyan"># And we will agree...</font>

02:05.680 --> 02:07.440
<font color="white"># Well, what is done...</font>

02:07.440 --> 02:09.560
<font color="white">SKIDDING AND CRASH</font>

02:09.560 --> 02:12.160
<font color="white"># And if you can't just shut up</font>
<font color="white">your mouth... #</font>

02:12.160 --> 02:14.160
<font color="cyan">Are you trying to get yourself</font>
<font color="cyan">killed?</font>

02:14.160 --> 02:15.760
<font color="white">HORN BEEPS</font>

02:17.200 --> 02:18.600
<font color="cyan">Come on. Move. Get out.</font>

02:18.600 --> 02:20.800
<font color="white">GOAT BLEATS</font>

02:23.120 --> 02:24.920
<font color="yellow">Can we go now?</font>

02:24.920 --> 02:26.400
<font color="cyan">Relax. We'll get there.</font>

02:28.360 --> 02:29.920
<font color="white">ENGINE STARTS</font>

02:31.880 --> 02:34.280
<font color="white">MUSIC CONTINUES</font>

02:46.440 --> 02:49.760
<font color="cyan">Here we are, ladies and gentlemen.</font>
<font color="cyan">Welcome to Honore.</font>

02:53.440 --> 02:54.560
<font color="white"># To be</font>

02:54.560 --> 02:56.840
<font color="cyan">Don't be shy!</font>

02:56.840 --> 02:58.400
<font color="white"># Or not to be</font>

03:01.080 --> 03:02.720
<font color="white"># That is the question... #</font>

03:04.320 --> 03:05.760
<font color="cyan">Oh, thank you.</font>

03:08.000 --> 03:10.280
<font color="white">ENGINE AND MUSIC STOP</font>

03:10.280 --> 03:14.080
<font color="lime">What time do you call this?</font>
<font color="lime">You were due in six minutes ago.</font>

03:14.080 --> 03:16.520
<font color="cyan">You're upset about six tiny minutes,</font>
<font color="cyan">Harold?</font>

03:16.520 --> 03:18.120
<font color="lime">A schedule is a schedule.</font>

03:18.120 --> 03:19.960
<font color="cyan">Well, I had to chase a goat</font>
<font color="cyan">off the road.</font>

03:19.960 --> 03:22.800
<font color="cyan">You know, I'm sure he waits for me,</font>
<font color="cyan">and it was hot as hell.</font>

03:22.800 --> 03:25.520
<font color="cyan">When you going to get the air-con</font>
<font color="cyan">fixed? </font><font color="lime">It's on the list.</font>

03:25.520 --> 03:27.440
<font color="cyan">On the list! Everything on the list.</font>

03:27.440 --> 03:29.320
<font color="cyan">Hey, you need to get off</font>
<font color="cyan">the bus now.</font>

03:29.320 --> 03:31.200
<font color="lime">Tell you what else is going</font>
<font color="lime">on the list.</font>

03:31.200 --> 03:34.200
<font color="lime">It's the third time you've been</font>
<font color="lime">late this week.</font>

03:34.200 --> 03:37.880
<font color="cyan">Sir, sir! You need to wake up.</font>

03:37.880 --> 03:39.280
<font color="cyan">I thought you was in a hurry.</font>

03:40.800 --> 03:42.240
<font color="cyan">Sir?</font>

03:42.240 --> 03:43.520
<font color="white">SHE SCREAMS</font>

04:16.480 --> 04:18.240
<font color="white">MUSIC IN VEHICLE</font>

04:18.240 --> 04:20.519
<font color="white"># Stay a little bit longer, she said</font>

04:20.519 --> 04:23.760
<font color="white"># Hold on, I'm coming</font>

04:23.760 --> 04:27.080
<font color="white"># Oh, yeah, stay a little bit longer</font>

04:29.320 --> 04:32.080
<font color="white"># Hold on, I'm coming... #</font>

04:32.080 --> 04:33.920
<font color="white">Danny La Rue, 52.</font>

04:35.960 --> 04:37.760
<font color="white">Dirty Gertie, number 30.</font>

04:37.760 --> 04:39.800
<font color="yellow">Sir? </font><font color="cyan">Ssh!</font>

04:41.200 --> 04:44.440
<font color="white">Stuck in a tree, 53. </font><font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

04:44.440 --> 04:47.720
<font color="white">Not now, Florence. This is the big</font>
<font color="white">one. We're playing for the foot spa.</font>

04:47.720 --> 04:49.760
<font color="white">Legs eleven.</font>

04:49.760 --> 04:51.960
<font color="yellow">Sir, we have a murder.</font>
<font color="white">HE SIGHS</font>

04:51.960 --> 04:54.400
<font color="white">I can't stop now. Look at them.</font>
<font color="yellow">We have to go.</font>

04:54.400 --> 04:56.440
<font color="white">They'll storm the stage.</font>
<font color="white">We'll never get out alive!</font>

04:56.440 --> 04:58.200
<font color="yellow">The Commissioner is already there.</font>

05:00.560 --> 05:03.000
<font color="white">19, 23, 7.</font>

05:03.000 --> 05:05.400
<font color="white">41, 12... </font><font color="lime">House!</font>

05:05.400 --> 05:07.200
<font color="white">Hooray!</font>

05:07.200 --> 05:10.680
<font color="white">Congratulations. Thank you, ladies.</font>
<font color="white">Same time next week.</font>

05:18.400 --> 05:19.440
<font color="cyan">Thank you.</font>

05:21.720 --> 05:23.680
<font color="cyan">Inspector.</font>

05:23.680 --> 05:26.320
<font color="white">Afternoon, JP. </font><font color="cyan">Afternoon, sir.</font>

05:26.320 --> 05:28.560
<font color="cyan">So what have we got?</font>
<font color="cyan">A 55-year-old man.</font>

05:28.560 --> 05:31.600
<font color="cyan">Name - Paul Raynor.</font>
<font color="cyan">Single stab wound to the chest.</font>

05:31.600 --> 05:34.240
<font color="cyan">Was found dead in the back seat</font>
<font color="cyan">of the bus by the driver.</font>

05:34.240 --> 05:37.280
<font color="cyan">The paramedics took him out of the</font>
<font color="cyan">bus as they tried to revive him.</font>

05:37.280 --> 05:39.880
<font color="white">Any sign of the knife? </font><font color="cyan">No.</font>
<font color="cyan">But the wound is quite big.</font>

05:39.880 --> 05:41.560
<font color="cyan">I'd say a six or seven inch blade.</font>

05:42.840 --> 05:46.240
<font color="white">There's fraying on his shirt there,</font>
<font color="white">just around the entry point.</font>

05:46.240 --> 05:49.360
<font color="yellow">So the blade was serrated.</font>
<font color="yellow">Like a hunting knife. </font><font color="white">Exactly.</font>

05:49.360 --> 05:52.120
<font color="white">Anything else? </font><font color="cyan">Yes. He had a few</font>
<font color="cyan">clothing items in a bag.</font>

05:52.120 --> 05:53.640
<font color="cyan">Small amount of cash in his pocket,</font>

05:53.640 --> 05:57.240
<font color="cyan">the bus ticket, and a driving</font>
<font color="cyan">licence, issued in Guadeloupe,</font>

05:57.240 --> 05:59.440
<font color="cyan">but ten years out of date.</font>

05:59.440 --> 06:01.040
<font color="white">Hang on. What's this?</font>

06:05.680 --> 06:07.160
<font color="white">A locker.</font>

06:07.160 --> 06:09.200
<font color="white">Or a padlock, maybe.</font>

06:09.200 --> 06:10.600
<font color="white">Check it for prints first.</font>

06:10.600 --> 06:14.000
<font color="white">Then finding what it fits</font>
<font color="white">might be quite useful. </font><font color="cyan">Yes, sir.</font>

06:14.000 --> 06:15.680
<font color="white">Was anyone with him on the bus?</font>

06:15.680 --> 06:17.600
<font color="cyan">Yes, there were three</font>
<font color="cyan">other passengers.</font>

06:17.600 --> 06:20.720
<font color="cyan">They're with the depot manager</font>
<font color="cyan">and the driver by the waiting room.</font>

06:20.720 --> 06:23.520
<font color="white">Any of them see anything?</font>
<font color="cyan">Apparently not.</font>

06:23.520 --> 06:26.240
<font color="lime">Inspector Mooney.</font>
<font color="lime">Good of you to come.</font>

06:26.240 --> 06:28.920
<font color="lime">I know it's your day off.</font>
<font color="white">Not a problem, sir.</font>

06:28.920 --> 06:32.080
<font color="white">When duty calls, you know me -</font>
<font color="white">I'm always available!</font>

06:32.080 --> 06:36.160
<font color="lime">I understand you were playing bingo.</font>
<font color="white">Yeah, you know... Baker's bun, 61!</font>

06:38.440 --> 06:40.600
<font color="white">Two little ducks, 22?</font>

06:42.360 --> 06:44.320
<font color="white">I'm the caller, you see.</font>

06:44.320 --> 06:47.280
<font color="lime">Carry on, Inspector. </font><font color="white">Yes, sir.</font>

06:48.600 --> 06:50.600
<font color="white">HE SIGHS</font>

06:52.520 --> 06:54.520
<font color="yellow">Bus or witnesses first?</font>

06:54.520 --> 06:55.720
<font color="white">Both, I think.</font>

06:55.720 --> 06:57.240
<font color="white">JP, everyone on the bus,</font>
<font color="white">if you would?</font>

06:57.240 --> 06:58.320
<font color="cyan">Yes, sir.</font>

07:02.600 --> 07:05.440
<font color="white">My uncle Ray was a bus driver</font>
<font color="white">in Donegal.</font>

07:05.440 --> 07:07.880
<font color="white">He used to drive one just like this.</font>

07:07.880 --> 07:10.280
<font color="white">There was a little stop bell.</font>

07:10.280 --> 07:12.720
<font color="white">BELL RINGS</font>
<font color="yellow">Sir?</font>

07:12.720 --> 07:15.800
<font color="white">Sorry. Back to the job in hand.</font>

07:15.800 --> 07:18.440
<font color="white">So, our victim was alone</font>
<font color="white">in the back seat</font>

07:18.440 --> 07:20.920
<font color="white">when the killer stabbed him</font>
<font color="white">in the chest,</font>

07:20.920 --> 07:23.520
<font color="white">without any of the passengers</font>
<font color="white">noticing it happened.</font>

07:23.520 --> 07:25.360
<font color="white">HE SIGHS</font>

07:25.360 --> 07:27.560
<font color="yellow">Sir, you've got something</font>
<font color="yellow">stuck to your knee.</font>

07:27.560 --> 07:31.440
<font color="white">Oh. What is it? Oh, here.</font>

07:31.440 --> 07:33.520
<font color="yellow">Hmm. </font><font color="cyan">Sir, the other passengers.</font>

07:33.520 --> 07:34.880
<font color="white">Good. Thank you, JP.</font>

07:37.520 --> 07:40.960
<font color="white">Well, my name is</font>
<font color="white">Detective Inspector Mooney,</font>

07:40.960 --> 07:43.440
<font color="white">this is Detective Sergeant Cassell,</font>

07:43.440 --> 07:45.560
<font color="white">and we'll try not to</font>
<font color="white">keep you very long.</font>

07:45.560 --> 07:47.920
<font color="white">But could I just start by asking you</font>
<font color="white">to please sit in the seats</font>

07:47.920 --> 07:49.960
<font color="white">that you were sitting in</font>
<font color="white">for the journey?</font>

07:57.600 --> 08:01.440
<font color="cyan">Sir, that's the depot manager,</font>
<font color="cyan">Mr Crane.</font>

08:01.440 --> 08:03.080
<font color="cyan">He met the bus as it arrived.</font>

08:03.080 --> 08:04.560
<font color="white">Could you do us a favour?</font>

08:04.560 --> 08:07.400
<font color="white">Could you be the murder victim</font>
<font color="white">and sit at the back of the bus?</font>

08:12.280 --> 08:15.120
<font color="white">This is where you were all sitting</font>
<font color="white">for the entire journey?</font>

08:15.120 --> 08:16.680
<font color="yellow">Yeah.</font>

08:16.680 --> 08:19.960
<font color="white">And did any of you know the victim,</font>
<font color="white">or each other, for that matter,</font>

08:19.960 --> 08:21.440
<font color="white">before you got on the bus?</font>

08:21.440 --> 08:23.560
<font color="lime">I never met him. </font><font color="cyan">Me neither.</font>

08:23.560 --> 08:24.760
<font color="white">I see.</font>

08:24.760 --> 08:26.600
<font color="white">It's fierce hot in here, isn't it?</font>

08:26.600 --> 08:29.000
<font color="lime">They air-con's broke,</font>
<font color="lime">but it's on the list.</font>

08:32.400 --> 08:37.120
<font color="white">Now, during the journey, did any of</font>
<font color="white">you move at any time at all?</font>

08:37.120 --> 08:38.480
<font color="cyan">No. </font><font color="white">No?</font>

08:38.480 --> 08:39.679
<font color="lime">I did.</font>

08:39.679 --> 08:40.919
<font color="white">But you were driving.</font>

08:40.919 --> 08:43.159
<font color="lime">Yeah, I had to stop.</font>
<font color="lime">There was a goat on the road.</font>

08:43.159 --> 08:45.720
<font color="white">A goat? </font><font color="lime">Yes, the road</font>
<font color="lime">above Angel Cove.</font>

08:45.720 --> 08:47.480
<font color="lime">I had to get out and chase him off.</font>

08:47.480 --> 08:48.640
<font color="white">And when you got back on,</font>

08:48.640 --> 08:50.480
<font color="white">could you still see the man</font>
<font color="white">at the back of the bus?</font>

08:50.480 --> 08:52.160
<font color="lime">Yes, he told me to hurry up.</font>

08:52.160 --> 08:54.880
<font color="lime">I said he should relax,</font>
<font color="lime">that we'd get there soon enough.</font>

08:54.880 --> 08:56.560
<font color="cyan">Can we go now?</font>

08:56.560 --> 08:58.200
<font color="lime">Relax! We'll get there!</font>

08:59.720 --> 09:02.120
<font color="white">So he was still alive</font>
<font color="white">when you drove away again?</font>

09:02.120 --> 09:03.240
<font color="lime">Definitely.</font>

09:03.240 --> 09:04.280
<font color="white">Oh.</font>

09:11.360 --> 09:13.000
<font color="white">DOOR OPENS</font>

09:17.240 --> 09:19.320
<font color="white">DOOR RATTLES</font>

09:26.800 --> 09:29.880
<font color="white">This emergency door, why can't it be</font>
<font color="white">opened from the outside?</font>

09:29.880 --> 09:31.360
<font color="lime">It's broke.</font>

09:31.360 --> 09:35.120
<font color="cyan">We're waiting for a part.</font>
<font color="cyan">It has to come from Germany.</font>

09:35.120 --> 09:38.600
<font color="yellow">So no-one could have got</font>
<font color="yellow">on the bus when it stopped.</font>

09:38.600 --> 09:42.840
<font color="white">So it's a direct route</font>
<font color="white">from the port to Honore,</font>

09:42.840 --> 09:47.120
<font color="white">and you all got on the bus together,</font>
<font color="white">and nobody else got on or off,</font>

09:47.120 --> 09:51.200
<font color="white">and everyone stayed in their own</font>
<font color="white">seats for the entire journey,</font>

09:51.200 --> 09:56.280
<font color="white">yet somehow Mr Raynor was stabbed</font>
<font color="white">without anyone seeing anything.</font>

10:04.800 --> 10:06.440
<font color="lime">All right if I head off early?</font>

10:06.440 --> 10:07.440
<font color="yellow">What do you think?</font>

10:07.440 --> 10:09.080
<font color="white">Right now, given everything we know,</font>

10:09.080 --> 10:11.720
<font color="white">there's only one possible</font>
<font color="white">explanation. </font><font color="yellow">Which is?</font>

10:11.720 --> 10:14.160
<font color="white">They're all in it together,</font>
<font color="white">the bus driver included -</font>

10:14.160 --> 10:15.760
<font color="white">maybe even the goat.</font>

10:15.760 --> 10:16.960
<font color="yellow">Do you believe that?</font>

10:16.960 --> 10:21.120
<font color="white">No, but nor do I believe that a man</font>
<font color="white">could be stabbed on that bus</font>

10:21.120 --> 10:22.680
<font color="white">without anyone seeing his killer.</font>

10:22.680 --> 10:24.120
<font color="cyan">Miss Brooks.</font>

10:24.120 --> 10:25.680
<font color="lime">Yes, Officer?</font>

10:25.680 --> 10:26.880
<font color="cyan">Your address, please?</font>

10:26.880 --> 10:28.840
<font color="lime">6A Mandela.</font>

10:28.840 --> 10:32.440
<font color="white">Now, everyone on the bus was also on</font>
<font color="white">the ferry, weren't they? </font><font color="yellow">Mm-hm.</font>

10:32.440 --> 10:35.000
<font color="white">So call the ferry company -</font>
<font color="white">they must have a security camera.</font>

10:35.000 --> 10:37.320
<font color="white">Let's see what the footage</font>
<font color="white">can tell us. </font><font color="yellow">Yes, sir.</font>

10:37.320 --> 10:39.720
<font color="white">And, JP, how are you getting</font>
<font color="white">on with that key?</font>

10:39.720 --> 10:42.200
<font color="cyan">Well, so far, we only have</font>
<font color="cyan">a fingerprint that matches</font>

10:42.200 --> 10:43.200
<font color="cyan">with the victim's.</font>

10:43.200 --> 10:45.960
<font color="cyan">There was a code on the key, which</font>
<font color="cyan">I've given to the manufacturers,</font>

10:45.960 --> 10:48.880
<font color="cyan">cos they think they can identify</font>
<font color="cyan">where it was sold,</font>

10:48.880 --> 10:50.720
<font color="cyan">but I'm just waiting for the call.</font>

10:50.720 --> 10:51.760
<font color="white">Grand.</font>

10:51.760 --> 10:53.640
<font color="white">And we're looking for a motive too,</font>

10:53.640 --> 10:56.240
<font color="white">so let's have a full background</font>
<font color="white">check on the victim.</font>

10:57.320 --> 10:59.080
<font color="white">Despite what they're all saying,</font>

10:59.080 --> 11:01.080
<font color="white">one of them must have known him.</font>

11:02.240 --> 11:03.360
<font color="white">Who's for a quick one?</font>

11:03.360 --> 11:04.920
<font color="yellow">Oh, I can't, sir. Sorry.</font>

11:07.920 --> 11:10.920
<font color="white">Just you and me, then, JP? </font><font color="cyan">Mm-hm.</font>

11:10.920 --> 11:14.720
<font color="white">But before I forget, tomorrow we</font>
<font color="white">should track the route the bus took.</font>

11:14.720 --> 11:17.320
<font color="white">No murder weapon was found</font>
<font color="white">when it got back to the depot,</font>

11:17.320 --> 11:19.840
<font color="white">so it could have been thrown from</font>
<font color="white">the window during the journey -</font>

11:19.840 --> 11:21.800
<font color="white">the part after the goat.</font>

11:21.800 --> 11:22.840
<font color="cyan">Yes, sir.</font>

11:40.120 --> 11:42.480
<font color="white">Have you heard from Dwayne at all?</font>

11:42.480 --> 11:45.560
<font color="white">How is the epic voyage</font>
<font color="white">with his dad going?</font>

11:45.560 --> 11:47.800
<font color="cyan">Well, I spoke to him yesterday, sir.</font>

11:47.800 --> 11:50.920
<font color="cyan">He was just off the coast of Cuba,</font>
<font color="cyan">and they had picked up the crew of</font>

11:50.920 --> 11:52.520
<font color="cyan">a motor yacht whose engine had died.</font>

11:52.520 --> 11:54.080
<font color="white">That's pretty heroic.</font>

11:54.080 --> 11:58.160
<font color="cyan">Mmm, that's what I thought, until</font>
<font color="cyan">I found out it was a hen party.</font>

11:58.160 --> 11:59.800
<font color="white">Typical. The luck of that man -</font>

11:59.800 --> 12:01.400
<font color="white">are you sure he's not Irish?</font>

12:06.880 --> 12:10.960
<font color="cyan">If I may say, sir, you're really</font>
<font color="cyan">taking to these bingo nights.</font>

12:10.960 --> 12:13.480
<font color="white">Oh, it's good to give</font>
<font color="white">something back.</font>

12:13.480 --> 12:17.440
<font color="white">To be honest, keeping myself busy of</font>
<font color="white">an evening is no bad thing.</font>

12:17.440 --> 12:20.800
<font color="white">I still can't quite get used to</font>
<font color="white">being on my own.</font>

12:20.800 --> 12:22.320
<font color="cyan">Missing Siobhan?</font>

12:22.320 --> 12:23.440
<font color="white">And her mum.</font>

12:25.360 --> 12:28.800
<font color="white">It's nearly three years now</font>
<font color="white">since Kathleen passed away.</font>

12:28.800 --> 12:31.480
<font color="white">It gets easier...bit by bit.</font>

12:31.480 --> 12:34.920
<font color="yellow">Jack, is Florence not with you?</font>

12:34.920 --> 12:37.720
<font color="white">Ah, no, I think she fancied</font>
<font color="white">an early night.</font>

12:37.720 --> 12:40.680
<font color="yellow">Oh, it's happening a lot lately.</font>

12:40.680 --> 12:42.640
<font color="yellow">I hope you're not</font>
<font color="yellow">working her too hard.</font>

12:48.520 --> 12:51.160
<font color="white">Have you noticed anything different</font>
<font color="white">about Florence, JP?</font>

12:51.160 --> 12:53.120
<font color="cyan">Like what?</font>

12:53.120 --> 12:55.040
<font color="white">Well, it's hard to</font>
<font color="white">put my finger on it.</font>

12:55.040 --> 12:57.040
<font color="white">Definitely something going on there.</font>

13:06.040 --> 13:08.040
<font color="lime">I thought you'd stood me up.</font>

13:08.040 --> 13:09.320
<font color="yellow">Mmm.</font>

13:10.480 --> 13:11.640
<font color="lime">Mmm. </font><font color="yellow">Mmm.</font>

13:11.640 --> 13:13.320
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. </font><font color="lime">Mm-hm.</font>

13:15.880 --> 13:17.960
<font color="yellow">There was a stabbing</font>
<font color="yellow">at the bus depot -</font>

13:17.960 --> 13:19.600
<font color="yellow">a man was killed.</font>

13:19.600 --> 13:21.640
<font color="lime">That's awful. </font><font color="yellow">Yeah.</font>

13:23.000 --> 13:27.720
<font color="lime">Although, as excuses go,</font>
<font color="lime">it's not bad.</font>

13:30.120 --> 13:32.200
<font color="lime">I've missed you. </font><font color="yellow">Since breakfast?</font>

13:32.200 --> 13:35.240
<font color="lime">What can I say? I'm obsessed.</font>

13:35.240 --> 13:37.680
<font color="lime">I've been thinking,</font>

13:37.680 --> 13:40.720
<font color="lime">isn't it time you introduced me to</font>
<font color="lime">the people you work with?</font>

13:40.720 --> 13:43.360
<font color="yellow">I will.</font>
<font color="lime">It doesn't have to be a big deal.</font>

13:43.360 --> 13:47.960
<font color="lime">I mean, I could just call by</font>
<font color="lime">one day and say hello.</font>

13:47.960 --> 13:49.080
<font color="lime">You know my friends.</font>

13:49.080 --> 13:51.880
<font color="yellow">I know. I'm just waiting for</font>
<font color="yellow">the right moment.</font>

14:01.840 --> 14:03.720
<font color="white">Morning, Grace.</font>
<font color="white">I missed you at the bingo.</font>

14:03.720 --> 14:05.800
<font color="cyan">Jack... </font><font color="white">I hope you had</font>
<font color="white">a good excuse.</font>

14:05.800 --> 14:07.320
<font color="yellow">Mr Jack. </font><font color="white">Ah, Dan...</font>

14:07.320 --> 14:08.520
<font color="yellow">Hey, hey.</font>

14:11.520 --> 14:13.360
<font color="white">Thanks, Jimmy. Put it on my tab.</font>

14:13.360 --> 14:15.280
<font color="lime">No worries, Jack.</font>

14:15.280 --> 14:17.080
<font color="cyan">Come on, man.</font>

14:18.720 --> 14:19.920
<font color="white">Morning, folks.</font>

14:19.920 --> 14:22.240
<font color="yellow">Morning, sir. </font><font color="cyan">Good morning, sir.</font>
<font color="white">Off out, JP?</font>

14:22.240 --> 14:23.680
<font color="cyan">I'm going to check the bus route.</font>

14:23.680 --> 14:26.440
<font color="white">Good man, and if your</font>
<font color="white">computer's still playing up,</font>

14:26.440 --> 14:27.760
<font color="white">just move to Dwayne's desk.</font>

14:27.760 --> 14:29.280
<font color="cyan">What, with all of his stuff there?</font>

14:29.280 --> 14:30.880
<font color="white">No, just pack it up.</font>
<font color="white">Put it in a box.</font>

14:30.880 --> 14:32.080
<font color="white">It'll be grand.</font>

14:37.000 --> 14:39.040
<font color="cyan">Erm, sir...</font>

14:39.040 --> 14:41.080
<font color="cyan">..I'll do it when I get back, OK?</font>

14:41.080 --> 14:42.880
<font color="white">As you like, JP.</font>

14:44.920 --> 14:47.360
<font color="white">Well, any news?</font>
<font color="white">Anything come through yet?</font>

14:47.360 --> 14:48.760
<font color="yellow">A little.</font>

14:48.760 --> 14:51.840
<font color="yellow">Butterfly Brown -</font>
<font color="yellow">single mother of three teenagers,</font>

14:51.840 --> 14:53.560
<font color="yellow">born and raised on the island.</font>

14:53.560 --> 14:54.720
<font color="yellow">Nothing prior.</font>

14:54.720 --> 14:56.440
<font color="white">Butterfly is unlikely to be</font>
<font color="white">our killer</font>

14:56.440 --> 14:58.600
<font color="white">because she was driving the bus.</font>

14:58.600 --> 15:00.360
<font color="yellow">Fiona Tait - she lives in London.</font>

15:00.360 --> 15:01.960
<font color="yellow">She says she's here on holiday.</font>

15:01.960 --> 15:04.720
<font color="yellow">Nothing previous.</font>
<font color="yellow">She looks like a typical tourist.</font>

15:04.720 --> 15:07.880
<font color="yellow">She's staying at a beach house</font>
<font color="yellow">at Delilah Cove.</font>

15:07.880 --> 15:11.120
<font color="yellow">Oliver Carr - ex-Army paratrooper.</font>

15:11.120 --> 15:13.960
<font color="yellow">His file says he was discharged</font>
<font color="yellow">from the forces,</font>

15:13.960 --> 15:18.040
<font color="yellow">following a court martial</font>
<font color="yellow">for striking a senior officer.</font>

15:18.040 --> 15:21.080
<font color="white">A man with a propensity for</font>
<font color="white">violence - now we're talking.</font>

15:21.080 --> 15:24.680
<font color="yellow">His business card says he's</font>
<font color="yellow">a private security consultant.</font>

15:24.680 --> 15:28.720
<font color="yellow">And finally we have Tamila Brooks,</font>
<font color="yellow">a resident of Saint Marie.</font>

15:28.720 --> 15:30.800
<font color="yellow">She works as a housemaid.</font>

15:30.800 --> 15:33.480
<font color="yellow">She was on her way back from</font>
<font color="yellow">visiting an aunt in Guadeloupe.</font>

15:33.480 --> 15:35.640
<font color="yellow">She's a very active member</font>
<font color="yellow">of the church.</font>

15:35.640 --> 15:37.600
<font color="white">And none of them have</font>
<font color="white">any links to the victim?</font>

15:37.600 --> 15:39.560
<font color="yellow">Nothing I can find.</font>

15:39.560 --> 15:41.600
<font color="white">COMPUTER CHIMES</font>
<font color="yellow">Oh.</font>

15:45.240 --> 15:49.000
<font color="yellow">But I think I can explain</font>
<font color="yellow">why his driving licence was</font>

15:49.000 --> 15:50.520
<font color="yellow">ten years out of date.</font>

15:52.080 --> 15:55.680
<font color="yellow">Paul Raynor had been in prison in</font>
<font color="yellow">Guadeloupe for the past 16 years.</font>

15:55.680 --> 15:57.440
<font color="yellow">He was released yesterday morning.</font>

15:57.440 --> 15:59.240
<font color="white">And what was he in prison for?</font>

15:59.240 --> 16:04.320
<font color="yellow">Murder - an armed robbery</font>
<font color="yellow">at the Ocean Casino in Guadeloupe.</font>

16:06.840 --> 16:09.360
<font color="yellow">was trying to get away.</font>

16:09.360 --> 16:12.240
<font color="yellow">Raynor was caught</font>
<font color="yellow">and arrested the next day.</font>

16:12.240 --> 16:14.920
<font color="white">So our victim was a man</font>
<font color="white">likely to have enemies.</font>

16:16.160 --> 16:17.920
<font color="yellow">Oh. </font><font color="white">What?</font>

16:17.920 --> 16:21.800
<font color="yellow">One of those enemies</font>
<font color="yellow">might be closer than we think.</font>

16:21.800 --> 16:24.800
<font color="yellow">The boy who died,</font>
<font color="yellow">his name was Philip Tait.</font>

16:29.320 --> 16:30.320
<font color="white">Tait...</font>

16:36.000 --> 16:39.600
<font color="cyan">The police victim support in England</font>
<font color="cyan">told me Paul Raynor</font>

16:39.600 --> 16:40.920
<font color="cyan">was being released.</font>

16:40.920 --> 16:44.480
<font color="cyan">I was in a trance for days, just...</font>

16:44.480 --> 16:49.080
<font color="cyan">It just didn't seem right that he'd</font>
<font color="cyan">be walking around in the sunshine.</font>

16:51.280 --> 16:53.680
<font color="cyan">So I booked a flight,</font>

16:53.680 --> 16:56.240
<font color="cyan">bought a knife on Guadeloupe,</font>
<font color="cyan">and followed him onto the ferry.</font>

16:57.880 --> 17:02.480
<font color="cyan">I almost did it but there were</font>
<font color="cyan">people in the way, children...</font>

17:02.480 --> 17:03.920
<font color="white">SHE INHALES</font>

17:03.920 --> 17:07.079
<font color="cyan">..and so I followed him</font>
<font color="cyan">onto the bus.</font>

17:07.079 --> 17:09.160
<font color="white">With the intention of murdering him?</font>

17:09.160 --> 17:10.240
<font color="cyan">Of course.</font>

17:11.480 --> 17:13.800
<font color="cyan">Philip was such a special boy.</font>

17:16.040 --> 17:20.880
<font color="cyan">He was on his gap year,</font>
<font color="cyan">off to see the world.</font>

17:20.880 --> 17:23.800
<font color="cyan">He'd done the Philippines,</font>
<font color="cyan">and the Far East,</font>

17:23.800 --> 17:27.079
<font color="cyan">and Australia and New Zealand,</font>

17:27.079 --> 17:29.840
<font color="cyan">and he was Caribbean island-hopping</font>
<font color="cyan">on his way back -</font>

17:29.840 --> 17:32.480
<font color="cyan">running out of money,</font>
<font color="cyan">of course, like they do.</font>

17:32.480 --> 17:36.960
<font color="cyan">So he, erm, got the odd bar job</font>
<font color="cyan">along the way.</font>

17:36.960 --> 17:38.880
<font color="yellow">He worked at the Ocean Casino?</font>

17:38.880 --> 17:41.440
<font color="cyan">Mmm, in the kitchens, yeah.</font>

17:41.440 --> 17:44.480
<font color="cyan">He said he quite enjoyed it.</font>

17:44.480 --> 17:46.520
<font color="cyan">Even talking about</font>
<font color="cyan">becoming a chef...</font>

17:48.560 --> 17:51.640
<font color="cyan">I said he could be</font>
<font color="cyan">anything he wanted to be.</font>

17:51.640 --> 17:54.640
<font color="white">I'm sorry for your loss,</font>
<font color="white">Mrs Tait, truly I am...</font>

17:54.640 --> 17:56.680
<font color="white">HE EXHALES</font>

17:56.680 --> 17:59.960
<font color="white">..but you must understand that what</font>
<font color="white">you've done is equally wrong.</font>

18:01.960 --> 18:05.200
<font color="white">Now, I'm afraid I'm going to have to</font>
<font color="white">ask you to surrender your passport.</font>

18:05.200 --> 18:07.000
<font color="white">SHE SNIFFLES</font>
<font color="cyan">Oh, yes, of course.</font>

18:10.400 --> 18:11.480
<font color="cyan">There we go.</font>

18:13.120 --> 18:17.200
<font color="yellow">Can we ask, how did you stab</font>
<font color="yellow">Mr Raynor on the bus</font>

18:17.200 --> 18:18.440
<font color="yellow">without being seen?</font>

18:19.560 --> 18:20.880
<font color="cyan">I didn't.</font>

18:22.880 --> 18:23.880
<font color="yellow">Excuse me?</font>

18:25.640 --> 18:26.720
<font color="cyan">I didn't kill him.</font>

18:28.000 --> 18:29.600
<font color="cyan">I mean, I wanted to.</font>

18:31.200 --> 18:35.320
<font color="cyan">I might even have found the courage</font>
<font color="cyan">to do it and happily shouted it</font>

18:35.320 --> 18:37.120
<font color="cyan">from the rooftops, but I didn't.</font>

18:38.320 --> 18:40.160
<font color="yellow">But you said you bought a knife.</font>

18:40.160 --> 18:43.000
<font color="cyan">I did, and then,</font>
<font color="cyan">after what happened,</font>

18:43.000 --> 18:45.560
<font color="cyan">I panicked and threw it</font>
<font color="cyan">into the sea yesterday.</font>

18:47.240 --> 18:50.920
<font color="cyan">Well, I had no further use for it.</font>
<font color="cyan">I mean, he was already dead.</font>

18:53.160 --> 18:54.560
<font color="white">HE EXHALES</font>

19:00.480 --> 19:02.520
<font color="white">ENGINE RUMBLES</font>

19:11.040 --> 19:12.720
<font color="yellow">Officer Hooper?</font>

19:12.720 --> 19:16.120
<font color="cyan">Oh, Commissioner,</font>
<font color="cyan">what are you doing here?</font>

19:16.120 --> 19:18.600
<font color="yellow">I was passing and saw your</font>
<font color="yellow">motorcycle unattended.</font>

19:18.600 --> 19:19.720
<font color="cyan">Oh, sir,</font>

19:19.720 --> 19:22.240
<font color="cyan">I'm just searching for the knife</font>
<font color="cyan">used to kill Paul Raynor, sir.</font>

19:22.240 --> 19:24.000
<font color="yellow">I see. </font><font color="cyan">Yeah.</font>

19:24.000 --> 19:25.640
<font color="yellow">Have you found it?</font>

19:25.640 --> 19:30.280
<font color="cyan">Possibly. Just beyond</font>
<font color="cyan">the ditch there, see?</font>

19:30.280 --> 19:32.080
<font color="cyan">I just can't seem to reach it, sir.</font>

19:32.080 --> 19:34.920
<font color="cyan">I may need to go and get some tools,</font>
<font color="cyan">you know, to cut the shrubs back.</font>

19:34.920 --> 19:36.600
<font color="yellow">Nonsense.</font>

19:36.600 --> 19:39.120
<font color="yellow">You hold it back -</font>
<font color="yellow">I'll get the knife.</font>

19:41.480 --> 19:43.520
<font color="yellow">I was a serving officer once,</font>
<font color="yellow">you know?</font>

19:46.040 --> 19:47.120
<font color="cyan">Oh.</font>

19:49.840 --> 19:51.040
<font color="cyan">This one.</font>

19:53.400 --> 19:54.400
<font color="cyan">Right.</font>

19:57.360 --> 19:58.360
<font color="cyan">All right.</font>

19:59.560 --> 20:01.200
<font color="white">ENGINE APPROACHES</font>

20:01.200 --> 20:02.200
<font color="cyan">Can you see it, sir?</font>

20:24.760 --> 20:26.520
<font color="yellow">We have enough to arrest her.</font>

20:26.520 --> 20:28.320
<font color="white">Well, we've got a great motive,</font>

20:28.320 --> 20:30.040
<font color="white">but if she did throw</font>
<font color="white">that knife in the sea,</font>

20:30.040 --> 20:31.320
<font color="white">we don't have a murder weapon.</font>

20:32.880 --> 20:36.280
<font color="white">And something she said</font>
<font color="white">about shouting it from the rooftops</font>

20:36.280 --> 20:38.480
<font color="white">if she had killed him -</font>

20:38.480 --> 20:42.080
<font color="white">as a parent, I believe that.</font>

20:42.080 --> 20:44.040
<font color="yellow">So what now?</font>

20:44.040 --> 20:45.120
<font color="white">JP!</font>

20:45.120 --> 20:49.000
<font color="cyan">Erm... We found it, sir!</font>

20:49.000 --> 20:50.560
<font color="cyan">It was right by the roadside...</font>

20:52.240 --> 20:53.920
<font color="cyan">..where you said.</font>

20:53.920 --> 20:57.040
<font color="yellow">Why would Fiona Tait say</font>
<font color="yellow">she'd thrown the knife in the sea</font>

20:57.040 --> 20:58.400
<font color="yellow">if she hadn't?</font>

20:58.400 --> 21:01.360
<font color="white">JP, left side or right</font>
<font color="white">as you head into Honore?</font>

21:01.360 --> 21:02.440
<font color="cyan">Erm...</font>

21:05.160 --> 21:07.200
<font color="white">JP EXHALES</font>

21:07.200 --> 21:09.040
<font color="cyan">Right side.</font>

21:09.040 --> 21:10.520
<font color="yellow">Fiona was sat on the left.</font>

21:10.520 --> 21:12.480
<font color="white">And Tamila Brooks.</font>

21:12.480 --> 21:16.120
<font color="white">The only person sitting on the right</font>
<font color="white">side of the bus was Oliver Carr.</font>

21:19.200 --> 21:20.600
<font color="white">So let me get this right,</font>

21:20.600 --> 21:25.080
<font color="white">you were sitting in the aisle</font>
<font color="white">opposite Mrs Tait and Miss Brooks?</font>

21:26.240 --> 21:27.520
<font color="cyan">Mm-hm.</font>

21:27.520 --> 21:28.920
<font color="cyan">I guess so, yeah.</font>

21:28.920 --> 21:30.560
<font color="yellow">And according to your statement,</font>

21:30.560 --> 21:33.320
<font color="yellow">you didn't see either of them</font>
<font color="yellow">move from their seats.</font>

21:33.320 --> 21:37.080
<font color="cyan">No, I wasn't paying them much</font>
<font color="cyan">attention, to be honest with you.</font>

21:37.080 --> 21:38.840
<font color="cyan">Why?</font>
<font color="cyan">Do you think one of them did it?</font>

21:38.840 --> 21:40.520
<font color="white">No, we don't think anything yet.</font>

21:42.000 --> 21:45.200
<font color="yellow">In your statement, you describe</font>
<font color="yellow">yourself as a security consultant.</font>

21:45.200 --> 21:46.200
<font color="cyan">That's right.</font>

21:46.200 --> 21:48.760
<font color="white">And what does that entail, exactly?</font>

21:48.760 --> 21:51.080
<font color="cyan">Consulting about security.</font>

21:53.160 --> 21:55.800
<font color="white">I suppose I asked for that.</font>

21:55.800 --> 22:00.240
<font color="cyan">Look, people ask me to check</font>
<font color="cyan">their personnel, building security,</font>

22:00.240 --> 22:01.640
<font color="cyan">that kind of thing, you know?</font>

22:01.640 --> 22:05.160
<font color="white">Yeah, things a military training</font>
<font color="white">would help with, I imagine.</font>

22:05.160 --> 22:07.920
<font color="cyan">You've seen my file. </font><font color="white">We have, yes.</font>

22:07.920 --> 22:12.440
<font color="white">You were discharged after</font>
<font color="white">assaulting a senior officer.</font>

22:12.440 --> 22:13.640
<font color="cyan">He had it coming.</font>

22:17.080 --> 22:18.440
<font color="cyan">Maybe we can help each other.</font>

22:18.440 --> 22:20.320
<font color="white">Really? And how would that work?</font>

22:20.320 --> 22:22.320
<font color="cyan">The man who was stabbed</font>
<font color="cyan">is called Paul Raynor.</font>

22:22.320 --> 22:24.960
<font color="cyan">He was released from prison</font>
<font color="cyan">yesterday morning in Guadeloupe.</font>

22:24.960 --> 22:28.280
<font color="white">We know. </font><font color="cyan">Yeah, he was convicted for</font>
<font color="cyan">armed robbery and murder</font>

22:28.280 --> 22:30.880
<font color="cyan">at the Ocean Casino in 2003.</font>

22:30.880 --> 22:32.080
<font color="white">We know that, too.</font>

22:32.080 --> 22:34.800
<font color="cyan">Well, yeah, what you probably don't</font>
<font color="cyan">know is that the money stolen</font>

22:34.800 --> 22:38.600
<font color="cyan">that night has never been recovered,</font>
<font color="cyan">so the Ocean Casino have hired me</font>

22:38.600 --> 22:42.480
<font color="cyan">to follow Raynor and see if</font>
<font color="cyan">there's anything left.</font>

22:43.640 --> 22:45.840
<font color="cyan">If it's here, I'll find it.</font>

22:45.840 --> 22:47.120
<font color="white">How much money?</font>

22:47.120 --> 22:48.360
<font color="cyan">750,000 euros.</font>

22:51.200 --> 22:53.200
<font color="cyan">And he was arrested the day</font>
<font color="cyan">after the robbery,</font>

22:53.200 --> 22:54.360
<font color="cyan">so not enough time to spend it.</font>

22:54.360 --> 22:57.520
<font color="yellow">And you think this money is why</font>
<font color="yellow">Mr Raynor was moving to Saint Marie?</font>

22:57.520 --> 23:01.400
<font color="cyan">That's what I was</font>
<font color="cyan">hoping to find out, yeah.</font>

23:01.400 --> 23:05.000
<font color="white">You followed him onto that bus</font>
<font color="white">believing he knew</font>

23:05.000 --> 23:08.880
<font color="white">the whereabouts of 750,000 euros,</font>

23:08.880 --> 23:10.360
<font color="white">and now he's dead.</font>

23:15.160 --> 23:17.800
<font color="white">So, Oliver Carr also knew</font>
<font color="white">the victim.</font>

23:17.800 --> 23:20.560
<font color="yellow">The money gives him the motive,</font>
<font color="yellow">and he's known to have been</font>

23:20.560 --> 23:22.080
<font color="yellow">violent in the past.</font>

23:22.080 --> 23:24.120
<font color="white">If it was the money he was after,</font>

23:24.120 --> 23:26.160
<font color="white">and that money is somewhere</font>
<font color="white">in Saint Marie,</font>

23:26.160 --> 23:27.240
<font color="white">why kill him on the bus?</font>

23:27.240 --> 23:30.200
<font color="yellow">Unless he already knew where it was,</font>
<font color="yellow">and just needed to stop him</font>

23:30.200 --> 23:32.280
<font color="yellow">getting there first.</font>

23:32.280 --> 23:34.280
<font color="white">Paul Raynor was arrested</font>
<font color="white">in Guadeloupe</font>

23:34.280 --> 23:35.880
<font color="white">the day after the robbery.</font>

23:35.880 --> 23:39.080
<font color="white">PHONE RINGS</font>
<font color="white">How did the money get to</font>
<font color="white">Saint Marie?</font>

23:39.080 --> 23:40.760
<font color="white">Get in touch with</font>
<font color="white">the Guadeloupe prison,</font>

23:40.760 --> 23:44.240
<font color="white">and find out who Raynor was in</font>
<font color="white">contact with while he was inside.</font>

23:44.240 --> 23:45.640
<font color="white">JP, what have you got for me?</font>

23:46.880 --> 23:48.960
<font color="white">The locker key?</font>
<font color="white">You know what it opens?</font>

23:51.760 --> 23:55.000
<font color="yellow">The manufacturers paired the key</font>
<font color="yellow">code to this set of lockers.</font>

23:55.000 --> 23:57.800
<font color="yellow">In fact, the manager recognised it</font>
<font color="yellow">straightaway.</font>

23:57.800 --> 23:59.440
<font color="white">Will we have a bet?</font>

23:59.440 --> 24:00.480
<font color="yellow">A bet?</font>

24:00.480 --> 24:03.960
<font color="white">On whether there's 750,000 euros</font>
<font color="white">in there or not. </font><font color="yellow">What?</font>

24:03.960 --> 24:07.000
<font color="white">First beer tonight says that locker</font>
<font color="white">is stuffed full of cash.</font>

24:08.200 --> 24:09.400
<font color="yellow">OK.</font>

24:28.320 --> 24:32.160
<font color="white">Why would Paul Raynor be</font>
<font color="white">carrying the key to a locker</font>

24:32.160 --> 24:34.800
<font color="white">containing nothing but a pair of</font>
<font color="white">budgie smugglers?</font>

24:34.800 --> 24:35.880
<font color="yellow">Budgie smugglers?</font>

24:35.880 --> 24:38.640
<font color="white">Yeah, it's a name we have for</font>
<font color="white">particularly small swimming trunks.</font>

24:38.640 --> 24:41.320
<font color="yellow">Yes, but why do you call them</font>
<font color="yellow">budgie smugglers?</font>

24:41.320 --> 24:43.560
<font color="white">Oh, because when they're...</font>

24:43.560 --> 24:45.960
<font color="white">I mean, when you...</font>

24:45.960 --> 24:47.800
<font color="white">You know, they sort of look...</font>

24:50.840 --> 24:52.000
<font color="white">In the olden days,</font>

24:52.000 --> 24:55.720
<font color="white">it's how pirates used to smuggle</font>
<font color="white">exotic birds into the country.</font>

24:55.720 --> 24:57.120
<font color="white">Yeah.</font>

24:57.120 --> 25:01.000
<font color="white">But the thing is they're not even</font>
<font color="white">his. They belong to Errol Porter.</font>

25:01.000 --> 25:03.840
<font color="white">Now, maybe if we can find him,</font>
<font color="white">he can enlighten us on what</font>

25:03.840 --> 25:07.280
<font color="white">a recently murdered armed robber was</font>
<font color="white">doing with his swimming trunks.</font>

25:07.280 --> 25:09.000
<font color="lime">I'll run a check, sir.</font>

25:09.000 --> 25:10.000
<font color="white">Commissioner?</font>

25:11.680 --> 25:13.600
<font color="cyan">You left a message this morning.</font>

25:13.600 --> 25:15.040
<font color="white">Yes, sir. We're a man down,</font>

25:15.040 --> 25:16.880
<font color="white">and, to be honest,</font>
<font color="white">we're a bit pushed.</font>

25:16.880 --> 25:20.720
<font color="cyan">I wasn't aware that Officer Myers</font>
<font color="cyan">actually did anything.</font>

25:20.720 --> 25:22.720
<font color="white">He was a valuable member of</font>
<font color="white">the team, sir.</font>

25:22.720 --> 25:24.600
<font color="cyan">It's a joke, Inspector.</font>

25:24.600 --> 25:25.760
<font color="white">A joke?</font>

25:25.760 --> 25:27.000
<font color="cyan">Yes.</font>

25:27.000 --> 25:28.360
<font color="white">Sorry, I missed that.</font>

25:30.040 --> 25:31.880
<font color="cyan">Are you saying I'm not funny?</font>

25:31.880 --> 25:33.920
<font color="white">Absolutely not, sir.</font>

25:33.920 --> 25:35.360
<font color="white">You're a very funny man.</font>

25:37.760 --> 25:41.000
<font color="white">You were doing it again there,</font>
<font color="white">weren't you?</font>

25:41.000 --> 25:45.080
<font color="cyan">I've already secured you a new</font>
<font color="cyan">officer for your team. </font><font color="white">Excellent.</font>

25:45.080 --> 25:47.240
<font color="cyan">The person I have selected</font>
<font color="cyan">is first-rate.</font>

25:47.240 --> 25:48.840
<font color="cyan">You are very lucky to get them.</font>

25:48.840 --> 25:50.720
<font color="white">Well, thank you, sir.</font>

25:50.720 --> 25:55.760
<font color="cyan">No need to thank me. That's my job.</font>
<font color="cyan">I'm the Police Commissioner.</font>

25:56.440 --> 25:57.680
<font color="white">Yes, you are.</font>

26:00.320 --> 26:03.400
<font color="cyan">This stabbing on the bus -</font>
<font color="cyan">can we expect an early conclusion?</font>

26:03.400 --> 26:05.400
<font color="white">We're making strong progress, sir.</font>

26:05.400 --> 26:07.840
<font color="cyan">Good. We don't want</font>
<font color="cyan">people to shy away</font>

26:07.840 --> 26:10.680
<font color="cyan">from using public transport, do we?</font>

26:10.680 --> 26:12.280
<font color="white">Heavens, no.</font>

26:18.600 --> 26:20.280
<font color="cyan">Budgie smugglers?</font>

26:22.560 --> 26:24.520
<font color="white">They're evidence, sir.</font>

26:24.520 --> 26:26.120
<font color="white">Believe it or not.</font>

26:26.120 --> 26:27.320
<font color="cyan">Carry on.</font>

26:35.440 --> 26:39.120
<font color="cyan">So, it looks like whoever we've got</font>
<font color="cyan">coming, we're lucky to get them.</font>

26:39.120 --> 26:40.960
<font color="white">So it would seem.</font>

26:40.960 --> 26:44.000
<font color="white">Right, well, let's regroup in</font>
<font color="white">the morning and see where we're at.</font>

26:44.000 --> 26:46.640
<font color="cyan">Er, I think I'll stay</font>
<font color="cyan">for a while, sir.</font>

26:46.640 --> 26:48.840
<font color="cyan">I've got some filing to do.</font>

26:48.840 --> 26:50.600
<font color="white">OK, well, enjoy your filing.</font>

26:50.600 --> 26:53.320
<font color="white">First thing tomorrow, please find</font>
<font color="white">me this Errol Porter, would you?</font>

26:53.320 --> 26:54.360
<font color="cyan">Yes, sir.</font>

26:54.360 --> 26:56.200
<font color="white">No idea what he's got to do with it.</font>

26:56.200 --> 26:57.800
<font color="white">But someone must know something.</font>

27:28.880 --> 27:30.880
<font color="white">HE SIGHS HEAVILY</font>

27:43.720 --> 27:45.680
<font color="cyan">Oh!</font>
<font color="white">HE CLEARS HIS THROAT</font>

27:49.440 --> 27:50.720
<font color="white">Harry! Breakfast!</font>

28:24.520 --> 28:26.160
<font color="white">Morning, Florence. How are you?</font>

28:27.160 --> 28:29.000
<font color="white">Yeah. No, just...</font>

28:29.000 --> 28:31.640
<font color="white">..just calling, I'm thinking of</font>
<font color="white">heading back to the crime scene.</font>

28:32.920 --> 28:35.280
<font color="white">Yeah. There's something</font>
<font color="white">I'd like to check.</font>

28:37.160 --> 28:38.840
<font color="white">OK, lovely.</font>

28:38.840 --> 28:40.200
<font color="white">Right. See you there.</font>

28:45.840 --> 28:47.680
<font color="white">You do know that's evidence</font>
<font color="white">in a murder case</font>

28:47.680 --> 28:48.920
<font color="white">you're contaminating there?</font>

28:59.080 --> 29:00.680
<font color="cyan">Can I help you?</font>

29:00.680 --> 29:03.000
<font color="white">Mr Crane. The very man.</font>

29:03.000 --> 29:05.960
<font color="white">These seats, you patch them up</font>
<font color="white">with black gaffer tape.</font>

29:05.960 --> 29:07.800
<font color="cyan">When we need to.</font>

29:07.800 --> 29:11.680
<font color="white">Only, I found a small piece, no</font>
<font color="white">more than a couple of inches square.</font>

29:11.680 --> 29:14.920
<font color="white">But I can't seem to find the tear</font>
<font color="white">it must have been covering.</font>

29:14.920 --> 29:17.960
<font color="cyan">Maybe the tear got bigger</font>
<font color="cyan">and I replaced it.</font>

29:17.960 --> 29:20.200
<font color="white">Ah, yes, that'll be it.</font>

29:43.960 --> 29:45.560
<font color="cyan">Is there anything else?</font>

29:46.600 --> 29:49.040
<font color="white">Oh, yes, a couple of things.</font>

29:49.040 --> 29:50.480
<font color="white">I just wrote them down somewhere.</font>

29:51.480 --> 29:52.880
<font color="white">Here we are.</font>

29:52.880 --> 29:55.280
<font color="white">Does the name Errol Porter</font>
<font color="white">ring any bells?</font>

29:55.280 --> 29:57.760
<font color="white">Just his name was in a pair of</font>
<font color="white">swimming trunks we found.</font>

29:57.760 --> 29:59.800
<font color="cyan">No. </font><font color="white">Not a former employee?</font>

29:59.800 --> 30:01.040
<font color="cyan">No.</font>

30:01.040 --> 30:03.200
<font color="white">Nothing at all? </font><font color="cyan">Nothing.</font>

30:04.680 --> 30:06.560
<font color="white">What about your driver - Miss Brown?</font>

30:06.560 --> 30:08.320
<font color="white">How long has she been with you?</font>

30:08.320 --> 30:13.200
<font color="cyan">We started up in 2004,</font>
<font color="cyan">and she joined us a year later.</font>

30:13.200 --> 30:14.560
<font color="white">Right.</font>

30:14.560 --> 30:16.240
<font color="white">We released the bus, didn't we?</font>

30:16.240 --> 30:19.280
<font color="cyan">The part for the emergency door</font>
<font color="cyan">arrived this morning, so we're</font>

30:19.280 --> 30:22.760
<font color="cyan">fixing that and the air-con, it</font>
<font color="cyan">should be back on the road tomorrow.</font>

30:22.760 --> 30:25.280
<font color="white">Well,</font>
<font color="white">better not hold you up any longer.</font>

30:29.440 --> 30:30.720
<font color="cyan">Yes, Mr Porter.</font>

30:30.720 --> 30:33.560
<font color="cyan">I'm just trying to establish whether</font>
<font color="cyan">you're the man I'm looking for.</font>

30:33.560 --> 30:35.360
<font color="cyan">There's, like, 11 of you</font>
