30:36.440 --> 30:38.200
<font color="cyan">Oh, great. Two for one.</font>

30:38.200 --> 30:39.640
<font color="cyan">So, can I ask,</font>

30:39.640 --> 30:42.880
<font color="cyan">does either you or your father</font>
