30:44.680 --> 30:45.960
<font color="cyan">Hello?</font>

30:47.280 --> 30:49.160
<font color="cyan">Can I help you?</font>

30:49.160 --> 30:50.400
<font color="white">Oh, I'm not sure.</font>

30:50.400 --> 30:53.880
<font color="white">I was just passing by and I thought</font>
<font color="white">I'd stop by and take a look.</font>

30:53.880 --> 30:55.880
<font color="white">I don't suppose Florence is here?</font>

30:55.880 --> 30:57.680
<font color="cyan">You know DS Cassell?</font>

