<font color="white">Well, we are...</font>

30:59.880 --> 31:01.880
<font color="cyan">You're the new guy.</font>

31:01.880 --> 31:03.800
<font color="white">Yes, I guess I am.</font>

31:03.800 --> 31:06.640
<font color="cyan">I'm JP Hooper, Jean-Pierre.</font>

31:06.640 --> 31:08.640
<font color="cyan">Just JP. </font><font color="white">Pleased to meet you, JP.</font>

31:08.640 --> 31:10.280
<font color="white">Patrice. Patrice Campbell.</font>

31:10.280 --> 31:12.920
<font color="cyan">Well,</font>
<font color="cyan">we weren't expecting you today.</font>

31:12.920 --> 31:15.960
<font color="white">No reason why you should.</font>
<font color="white">Like I said, I was just passing.</font>

31:17.600 --> 31:18.800
<font color="white">You know about me, then?</font>

31:18.800 --> 31:20.240
<font color="cyan">Oh, yeah, we found out yesterday.</font>

31:20.240 --> 31:21.440
<font color="white">Oh, great.</font>

31:21.440 --> 31:23.440
<font color="white">Yeah, I thought I'd come in</font>
<font color="white">and say hello.</font>

31:23.440 --> 31:24.960
<font color="cyan">Yes, well,</font>
<font color="cyan">the inspector is not here,</font>

31:24.960 --> 31:26.760
<font color="cyan">he'll be very sorry he missed you.</font>

31:26.760 --> 31:29.160
<font color="white">No worries.</font>
<font color="white">I'll catch him next time.</font>

31:31.600 --> 31:33.800
<font color="cyan">I guess you know you've got some</font>
<font color="cyan">big shoes to fill, right?</font>

31:33.800 --> 31:35.360
<font color="white">Oh.</font>

31:36.800 --> 31:39.120
<font color="cyan">The guy before you, he was amazing.</font>

31:39.120 --> 31:40.240
<font color="cyan">You know?</font>

31:40.240 --> 31:41.840
<font color="white">The guy before me?</font>

31:41.840 --> 31:42.840
<font color="cyan">Yeah.</font>

31:42.840 --> 31:44.600
<font color="cyan">Not to say you're not.</font>

31:44.600 --> 31:45.840
<font color="cyan">But he was just...</font>

31:45.840 --> 31:47.200
<font color="cyan">You know, he was great.</font>

31:48.480 --> 31:50.280
<font color="cyan">One of the best, in fact.</font>

31:50.280 --> 31:53.120
<font color="white">Oh, I'm not sure Florence</font>
<font color="white">has mentioned him.</font>

31:53.120 --> 31:56.000
<font color="cyan">That surprises me.</font>
<font color="cyan">They were very close.</font>

31:56.000 --> 31:57.640
<font color="cyan">And he hasn't been gone long.</font>

31:57.640 --> 31:58.960
<font color="cyan">In fact, just yesterday,</font>

31:58.960 --> 32:01.680
<font color="cyan">she was just saying how much</font>
<font color="cyan">she can't wait for him to come back.</font>

32:01.680 --> 32:04.520
<font color="cyan">But, still, you can keep everything</font>
<font color="cyan">warm for him.</font>

32:04.520 --> 32:06.360
<font color="cyan">Can't you?</font>

32:06.360 --> 32:07.480
<font color="white">Hm.</font>

32:13.440 --> 32:15.080
<font color="yellow">CCTV from the ferry.</font>

32:15.080 --> 32:17.120
<font color="white">Great, Florence.</font>
<font color="white">Let's get back and take a look.</font>

32:17.120 --> 32:18.720
<font color="yellow">Anything new?</font>

32:18.720 --> 32:20.760
<font color="white">At the moment, we just have</font>
<font color="white">a collection of stuff</font>

32:20.760 --> 32:22.440
<font color="white">that doesn't make any sense.</font>

32:22.440 --> 32:24.240
<font color="white">A woman who bought a knife</font>

