32:37.840 --> 32:40.120
<font color="white">we found a pair of mouldy</font>
<font color="white">swimming trunks.</font>

32:40.120 --> 32:41.320
<font color="yellow">Budgie smugglers. </font><font color="white">Exactly.</font>

