33:35.920 --> 33:37.560
<font color="white">And I'm guessing this wasn't it?</font>

33:37.560 --> 33:38.720
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

33:40.000 --> 33:41.440
<font color="cyan">It's for you.</font>

33:44.840 --> 33:46.520
<font color="yellow">DS Cassell.</font>

33:56.240 --> 33:57.680
<font color="lime">Hey, Harold.</font>

33:59.200 --> 34:00.920
<font color="lime">I saw the police were back.</font>

34:00.920 --> 34:03.160
<font color="lime">What sort of things were they</font>
<font color="lime">asking you about?</font>

34:03.160 --> 34:05.400
<font color="cyan">Why do you want to know?</font>

34:05.400 --> 34:07.960
<font color="cyan">Nothing to hide, have you,</font>
<font color="cyan">Butterfly?</font>

34:17.080 --> 34:19.600
<font color="yellow">Yes, well, thank you very much. Bye.</font>

34:21.199 --> 34:23.360
<font color="yellow">OK, sir, that was</font>
<font color="yellow">the assistant governor</font>

34:23.360 --> 34:25.159
<font color="yellow">from the prison in Guadeloupe.</font>

34:25.159 --> 34:27.320
<font color="yellow">He had some very interesting</font>
<font color="yellow">information to pass on</font>

34:27.320 --> 34:28.920
<font color="yellow">about Paul Raynor.</font>

34:28.920 --> 34:31.280
<font color="white">Really? Well, I'm all ears,</font>
<font color="white">Florence.</font>

34:31.280 --> 34:34.239
<font color="yellow">Firstly, in the week</font>
<font color="yellow">before Mr Raynor was released,</font>

34:34.239 --> 34:37.080
