<font color="cyan">I can check it out.</font>

34:54.560 --> 34:56.800
<font color="white">Good on you, JP,</font>
<font color="white">see what you can find.</font>

34:56.800 --> 34:58.640
<font color="white">Anything else from your chat</font>
<font color="white">with the prison?</font>

34:58.640 --> 35:02.040
<font color="yellow">Apparently, Paul Raynor received</font>
<font color="yellow">an increasing amount of regular mail</font>

